cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.ST

This paper deals with machine learning and classification, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of empirical risk-based methods, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The analysis of the data and the incorporation of the labeling mechanism is relevant to computer vision, which is covered by cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the assumptions made in learning from positive and unlabeled data, which is related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.ST (Statistics).
